page.title: 08NEWLAND PARK, 2.
page.content: In another garden there was a yacht. The gardens are so big that some of the occupants have sold the side part of their garden so that another house could be built in the space. Even these new houses are big and have large gardens. The people who live in{Newland Park} are very rich. Just about down every drive there are at least two cars. They are professional people like doctors and solicitors. In one of the houses there is a nursery for lots of young children. The houses are privately owned. We think that the people who live in these houses are very lucky.
